[32m+[m[32mDatabase/ORM | :x: | :x: | :heavy_check_mark:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mDon't bother choosing the right starter:[m
[32m+[m[32mYou can easily add/remove a Node.js server and add/remove a database/ORM.[m
