[32m+[m[32m1. Install the Reframe CLI.[m
[32m+[m[32m   ~~~shell[m
[32m+[m[32m   $ npm install -g @reframe/cli[m
[32m+[m[32m   ~~~[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m2. Initialize a new Rreframe app.[m
[32m+[m[32m   ~~~shell[m
[32m+[m[32m   $ reframe init my-app[m
[32m+[m[32m   ~~~[m
[32m+[m[32m   A `my-app/` directory is created and populated with a scaffold.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m3. Build the pages and start the server.[m
[32m+[m[32m   ~~~shell[m
[32m+[m[32m   $ cd my-app[m
[32m+[m[32m   $ reframe start[m
[32m+[m[32m   ~~~[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m4. Open [http://localhost:3000](http://localhost:3000).[m
